reviewText: Witches' Brew saw Lana doing a fine job as the witch Vivian. Lots of fun seeing her act with Richard Benjamin and Teri Garr. Fun to see an actress go out on a high note.
A fun movie with lots of comedy. Interesting take on witches. Terri Garr was good in this movie.
Received quickly.  Have not had a chance to watch the movie but if the condition of the movie is as good as their service I will be a returning customer.
I LIKED THE MOVIE, IT WAS A FUNNY MOVIE ON WITCHCRAFT. I LIKE TERRI GARR, AND RICHARD BENJAMIN,. IT WAS A FUN MOVIE.
